Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是想吓你\N但加兰之前失踪过.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna aIarm you\Nbut GarIand has disappeared before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:57.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰的事总是和工作有关.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granted it's aIways been work-reIated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员,\N这次也可能和工作有关吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper,\Ndid this seem work-reIated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太太, 那很难说.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, that's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:12.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 贝蒂, 你是说这种情形\N也是少校工作的一部分吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Betty, you're saying this behavior\Nis part of the way the major operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我这样说吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是突然不见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he Ieave suddenIy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 他突然就不见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们当时正闲谈着,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were speaking phiIosophicaIIy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我离开营地\N去小解.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I Ieft the campsite\Nto answer the caII of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来的时候他就不见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I returned he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上,你进了林子里\N是十分有意味的暗示.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you were in the woods\Nis very significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哪方面?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他常常,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ConfidentiaIIy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在私下谈起过它们.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he taIks about them constantIy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太太, 少校他--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, has the major--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,无疑, 他是个\N意识很前卫的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIearIy, a man\Nof no smaII spirituaI advancement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一直尝试接触那些\N在林子里存活的未知生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--been attempting to contact\Nsome eIement that Iives in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是他最高机密工作的一部分吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a part of his top-secret work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是指定机密.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cIassified.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 那他一定具有文艺复兴般的情欲\N去一探究竟, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WeII, he certainIy has a renaissance\Npassion for expIoration, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那样看自己的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how he sees himseIf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对此没有指引可循.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no manuaI for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没有任何相关的指引\N可以遵循.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's certainIy no manuaI\Nto be married to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,贝蒂, 谢谢你来.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betty, thanks for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们目前只能是\N提高警觉,密切关注事态发展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, there's not much more\Nwe can do right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外, 我们也别无他法了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except, keep our eyes peeIed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:34.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰在床头桌上\N留了些纸条. 我把它们传真过来吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GarIand Ieft some notes on his bedside\NtabIe. I can caII you back with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它们可能非常有用.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might be very heIpfuI.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少校这次突发离开\N或许不止是有关工作那么简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, the major didn't just wander off\Non some work-reIated assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:52.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的那束闪光, 是存在森林\N里一股强大力量.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fIash of Iight I saw, it's a powerfuI\Nforce that exists in those woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长, 我们买到了\N安先生和妙福太太的结婚礼物.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff, we found Mr. and Mrs. MiIford's\Nwedding present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:04.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是围巾和领结情侣套装.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matching scarf and ascot set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.\N我上次还欠他一份礼呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.\NI stiII owe him a gift from Iast time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:11.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不敢相信\N他又结婚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't beIieve\Nthat he's getting married again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜奇的婚事是季节性发情\N就像鲑鱼回潮.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dougie's weddings are a seasonaI\Nthing. Like the return of the saImon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来也匆匆, 去也匆匆.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry in haste, repent in Ieisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}你好, 警长?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}戴尔·库尔帕来电.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a call for a Dale Crewper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}长途. 我希望我没把它挂掉.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long distance. l hope l didn't cut it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:31.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,临时工. 露西帮妙福\N筹备婚礼去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temp. Lucy's heIping out\Nwith the MiIford wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库? 我们在哪儿?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是戈登·寇尔\N我在本德,俄勒冈州.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gordon Cole calling\Nfrom Bend, Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗, 戈登?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Gordon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:43.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}库, 我打电话来是想跟你说\N这次内部调查的事{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, l just called to say\Nthat you have my full support
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我会全力支持你.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this investigation business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}艰难时期\N但我们会熬过去的.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are hard times\Nbut we get through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 谢谢你, 戈登.\N- 我也身受其害.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you, Gordon.\N- lt ranks poor with me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在, 库, 有哪些是真的?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Coop, is any of this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}杀死2人?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double homicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}毒品被盗?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stolen drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}妓寨械斗?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Storming a whorehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简直是一派胡言.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's aII a bunch of hogwash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我不得不通知你\N毒品监察部{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to tell you\Nthe Drug Enforcement Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}开始四处打探了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is starting to nose around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}他们派出了一个顶级探员\N去调查毒品的事了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sending down a top dog\Nto investigate the drug angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们派了谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they sending?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是戈登.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是戈登·寇尔.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Gordon Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是问那个密探是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}丹尼斯·莱森.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dennis Bryson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是莱森. 他是个好人, 哈里.\N不会胡来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bryson. He's a good man, Harry.\NNo nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}别让他搞乱你, 库.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him rattle you, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这些家伙专靠\N抄别人家老底为生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys make a living looking\Nthrough other people's drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我们时不时,\N就会有些把柄.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've all had our socks\Ntossed around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}被他们抓在手上.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}给你个忠告:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couple of words of advice:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}笑脸迎人.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let a smile be your umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 谢谢, 戈登.\N- 再见, 库.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks, Gordon.\N- See you, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 哈里...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WeII, Harry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...准备直面事实吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...time to face the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,早安, 罗杰.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GentIemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经知道控罪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望以什么\N为你自己辩护呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wish to present\Nas your defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有辩护.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信我的行动\N是正确的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am compIeteIy confident\Nin the rightness of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:28.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至于某些事件有违局里的指导方针\N我将为此负全责.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of it occurred outside of Bureau\NguideIines, I wiII pay the price for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是清白的\N没有犯下有违道德的罪行.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm innocent\Nof any criminaI wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们执意要指控我的话,\N那我们就在法庭上见吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they wish to charge me,\NI wiII defend myseIf in a court of Iaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DaIe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有2种方法去处理这次事件\N正途或歪路.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a right way and a wrong way\Nto do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而首先我们预期的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the first thing we expect
