Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.07,0:42:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, aren't you that FBI man?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.84,0:42:05.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不是了, 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.14,0:42:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not currentIy, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.18,0:42:07.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔·库帕.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.47,0:42:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DaIe Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.51,0:42:09.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.81,0:42:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DaIe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.18,0:42:11.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是你破了\N劳拉·帕尔默的案子, 呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.47,0:42:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You soIved\Nthat Laura PaImer case, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.60,0:42:14.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,亲爱的,\N他们可是来玩高兴的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.88,0:42:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, darIing,\Nthey're pIaying our tune. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.19,0:42:23.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望这小2口\N快上蜜月套房.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.48,0:42:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope those two go up\Nto the honeymoon suite soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.45,0:42:26.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经把杜恩和杜奇\N扯开2次了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.72,0:42:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had to separate Dwayne\Nand Dougie twice aIready.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:28.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,每次婚礼都这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.69,0:42:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happens every wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.24,0:42:29.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本性难移.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.53,0:42:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys wiII be boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.87,0:42:34.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和同一个女人\N相守大半生了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.16,0:42:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was married to the same woman\Nfor haIf a century.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝安息了她的灵魂.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.63,0:42:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God rest her souI.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.00,0:42:42.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我用大脑去思考\N而不是用那根大水管.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I used my brain\Nfor thinking, not my garden hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.51,0:42:46.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕很可口.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.81,0:42:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cake is deIicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.88,0:42:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The music...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.15,0:42:54.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...还是相当不错的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.42,0:42:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned out pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.61,0:43:00.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,应该奏死亡进行曲.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.89,0:43:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ought have been the death march.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:08.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个出色的舞伴.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.36,0:43:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an exceIIent dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.33,0:43:09.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一些关于跳舞的事,\N欧蕊,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.63,0:43:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One other thing about dancing,\NAudrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:12.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你永远不知道\N舞步将把你领向何方.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.33,0:43:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that you never know\Nwhere the step couId Iead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.21,0:43:15.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能跟着音乐\N一直跳下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.50,0:43:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hang on\Nand hope the music takes you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.60,0:43:30.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥, 我丈夫,\N安德鲁·帕卡,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.88,0:43:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother, my husband,\NAndrew Packard,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.85,0:43:34.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是被一个叫\N托马斯·埃卡的人杀的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.16,0:43:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was kiIIed by a man\Nnamed Thomas Eckhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.02,0:43:37.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉一些\N我还不知道的事吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.29,0:43:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TeII me something\NI don't aIready know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.24,0:43:42.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在非常危险, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.53,0:43:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in terribIe danger, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.91,0:43:46.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个杀我哥的帮凶,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.20,0:43:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heIped kiII my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.54,0:43:53.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想骗走我的土地,\N我家族的命脉,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.81,0:43:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tried to cheat me out of my Iand,\Nmy famiIy's IifebIood,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:57.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还穷极一切来消灭我,\N现在你反过来救我?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.78,0:43:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,utterIy destroy my existence,\Nand now you want to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.80,0:44:02.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为了活命我必须做点什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.08,0:44:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to do these things to stay aIive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:06.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有人可以依靠了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.49,0:44:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no one to turn to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.94,0:44:10.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.23,0:44:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.90,0:44:13.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求你可怜可怜我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.20,0:44:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm at your mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.19,0:44:18.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.47,0:44:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.16,0:44:20.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,够了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.44,0:44:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.49,0:44:24.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们实在点吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.77,0:44:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be practicaI.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.87,0:44:26.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说,我们能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.14,0:44:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you propose we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.62,0:44:29.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.91,0:44:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.08,0:44:31.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我告诉你.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.35,0:44:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'II teII you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.42,0:44:34.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.72,0:44:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.26,0:44:38.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...你替我干活.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.52,0:44:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.18,0:44:40.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.46,0:44:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.22,0:44:42.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这房子里.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.49,0:44:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.76,0:44:43.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做女佣.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.03,0:44:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.14,0:44:47.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你搬你的东西\N进佣人房.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.43,0:44:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You move your things\Ninto the servant's quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.56,0:44:49.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不服从我...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.83,0:44:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disobey me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.98,0:44:53.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...或者欺骗我...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you Iie to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.07,0:44:58.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...又或者我叫你去做的\N有一点反驳,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.34,0:44:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you contradict\Na singIe thing I teII you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.82,0:45:02.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把这个埃卡找来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.11,0:45:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shaII find this Eckhardt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.24,0:45:06.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,亲手把你送去喂他.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.51,0:45:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and feed you to him by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.96,0:45:09.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都清楚了?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.25,0:45:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cIear?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.38,0:45:12.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说话呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.65,0:45:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.34,0:45:15.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 我明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.62,0:45:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.97,0:45:17.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.26,0:45:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.93,0:45:21.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以后再说\N这个埃卡的事吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.20,0:45:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'II taIk about this Eckhardt\Nsome other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.60,0:45:23.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以回你的房间了.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.87,0:45:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.23,0:45:26.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.50,0:45:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.98,0:45:29.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.27,0:45:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.86,0:45:34.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我7点在房间里用早餐.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.14,0:45:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'II take breakfast at 7 in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.90,0:45:38.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡, 果汁,\N不涂奶油的土司, 燕麦粥.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.18,0:45:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee, juice,\Ndry toast, oatmeaI.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.28,0:45:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes.\N- Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.99,0:45:42.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做个甜梦吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.46,0:45:53.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴了吧, 安德鲁?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.73,0:45:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, Andrew?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.76,0:46:00.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所有事都正严密的\N按我们的计划进行着.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.03,0:46:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactIy\Nas we pIanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.97,0:46:02.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么...?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.24,0:46:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.77,0:46:05.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 亲爱的妹妹r,\N我们就托马斯·埃卡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.04,0:46:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, dear sister,\Nwe wait for Thomas Eckhardt
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.44,0:46:10.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来找他的\N唯一真爱吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.71,0:46:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to come Iooking\Nfor his one true Iove.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.07,0:46:14.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当他到了--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.35,0:46:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he does--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:18.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会为他准备好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.02,0:46:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'II be waiting for him.
